uation are also established, and those can be viewed as a new class\nof nonlocal partial differential equations in bounded domains.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 21 Jan 2022 17:28:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Nov 2022 16:12:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-07"}
